    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Drain pump per drawer (Double DishDrawer independent)</h3><p>Each drawer has its own independent drain pump on Double DishDrawer. Swap $280–$420 per drawer pump.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Drawer guide + rail service</h3><p>Drawer sliding mechanism wears at 6-10 years. Guide + rail service $180–$280.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Flexible drain hose wear at stress points</h3><p>The hose flexes every drawer cycle and wears at specific bend points. Service $160–$260.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Drawer-seal compromise</h3><p>Water leaks into cabinetry during drain cycle — seal fault. Full seal service $320–$460.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Drawer-position sensor faults</h3><p>Sensor tells control board whether drawer is fully closed. Failure produces won't-start or mid-cycle stop. Sensor $180–$280.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>F&amp;P-specialty control board</h3><p>Platform-specific control board, doesn't cross-reference with mainstream US brands. $440–$620 swap, 5-10 day specialty parts lead.</p></div>
